  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effect of colchicine on high sensitivity
      C-reactive protein (hs-CRP), a blood marker to measure inflammation, in patients with acute
      coronary syndromes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
